<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf400d81-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s11317"><num value="11317">§ 11317.</num><heading> Definitions</heading>
<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">For purposes of this subchapter:</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idbf400d82-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s11317/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> The term “Council” means the United States Interagency Council on Homelessness established in <ref href="/us/usc/t42/s11311">section 11311 of this title</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idbf400d83-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s11317/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> The term “Federal agency” has the meaning given the term “agency” in <ref href="/us/usc/t5/s551/1">section 551(1) of title 5</ref>.</content>
</paragraph>
<sourceCredit id="idbf400d84-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/100/77/tII/s207">Pub. L. 100–77, title II, § 207</ref>, <date date="1987-07-22">July 22, 1987</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/101/489">101 Stat. 489</ref>; <ref href="/us/pl/108/199/dG/tII/s216/4">Pub. L. 108–199, div. G, title II, § 216(4)</ref>, <date date="2004-01-23">Jan. 23, 2004</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/118/394">118 Stat. 394</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
<notes type="uscNote" id="idbf400d85-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" role="crossHeading" topic="editorialNotes" id="idbf400d86-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered"><b>Editorial Notes</b></heading></note>
<note style="-uslm-lc:I74" topic="amendments" id="idbf400d87-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa"><heading class="centered smallCaps">Amendments</heading><p style="-uslm-lc:I21" class="indent0">2004—Par. (1). <ref href="/us/pl/108/199">Pub. L. 108–199</ref> substituted “United States Interagency Council on Homelessness” for “Interagency Council on the Homeless”.</p>
</note>
</notes>
